<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="employment-n">employment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪm'plɔɪmənt/    美 /ɪm'plɔɪmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 雇用；聘用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mexican law prohibits the employment of children under 14. 
墨西哥法律禁止雇用14岁以下的儿童。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 职业；工作；就业：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>out of employment 
失业</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>create <strong>employment opportunities</strong> 
创造就业机会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>full-time</strong> / <strong>part-time employment</strong>
全职/兼职工作</p></div></div>